{
  "stem": "8359.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's us.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I-- they had a few German civilians working there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of war.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Young people, right?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how we even communicated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I certainly-- to this day, I don't know French, and I don't care.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a couple woman-man interaction, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know that it went that far, because there was just no place to do-- [LAUGHS]-- to do it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the feelings-- the feelings were there, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Feelings were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terrible in that--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Haza. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think triple bunks we had at that point already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't tell you this, because they kept constantly sending us people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, alone-- alone-- on a straw--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mattress, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's-- that's what you-- that's what I had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had-- oh-- postcards that were written by my sister and my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this picture of my sister and my niece and her friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did hide them when I knew that we were going to have an inspection, because we weren't allowed to have anything like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we never knew, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We'd like find out in the last minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I wouldn't say days a week.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know, maybe a couple, few times a month.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It depends, you know, whether they were just talking to the commandant or whether they wanted to see the--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, snow, rain, heat, whatever, you stood out there, and they counted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they were missing, they counted again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they were missing, they counted again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sometimes an hour, hour and a half.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, and by then, we wore sort of a uniform already.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
